    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/d0ae58a6dbc2a103effae34c7e74a1f6.poster.avif?t=1759337542\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/d0ae58a6dbc2a103effae34c7e74a1f6.webm?t=1759337542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/d0ae58a6dbc2a103effae34c7e74a1f6.mp4?t=1759337542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the classics of the genre, such as the original Resident Evil and Koudelka, <strong>Vampire Huntress - Lament of the Sun</strong> brings you the classic survival horror experience, where every bullet - and stake - counts. Make difficult decisions of what to bring with you, and what to leave in storage. What enemies to dispatch and what to avoid. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust the experience based on your preferences, with settings for limited saves, auto-targeting, inventory size, and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/bb16f6ed5ab00cc3ba273c8d994fa450.poster.avif?t=1759337542\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/bb16f6ed5ab00cc3ba273c8d994fa450.webm?t=1759337542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/bb16f6ed5ab00cc3ba273c8d994fa450.mp4?t=1759337542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through the vast interconnected world of <strong>Vampire Huntress</strong>, in and around the massive Castle Whitecairn. Solve puzzles, find secrets and shortcuts and collect items necessary for your continued survival. As you explore the world, you will face enemies each more dangerous and fierce than the last! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/25686bac97a552426713d56b79a220df.poster.avif?t=1759337542\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/25686bac97a552426713d56b79a220df.webm?t=1759337542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/25686bac97a552426713d56b79a220df.mp4?t=1759337542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the dark fantasy world of <strong>Vampire Huntress - Lament of the Sun</strong> as you play as Luna Ashcroft, a vampire in search for answers. Her betrothed, Lord Voltarius, has returned after 1000 years  and set in motion a plan that not only shakes Luna personally, but threatens to also shake the very foundation of existence.<br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/994905836b32b3d49cf59c4aa6acf7eb.poster.avif?t=1759337542\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/994905836b32b3d49cf59c4aa6acf7eb.webm?t=1759337542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212500/extras/994905836b32b3d49cf59c4aa6acf7eb.mp4?t=1759337542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic survival horror experience</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interconnected world focused on exploration</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inventory and resource management</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles and secrets</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modern controls and Tank controls </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjustable difficulty settings such as Limited Saves and Inventory Management</p></li></ul>",
